videos.headline: Navy scores first with 91-yard TD
videos.description: Running back Malcolm Perry shoots up the middle and breaks free for a 91-yard touchdown, as Navy takes an early 7-0 lead on Air Force.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Navy scores first with 91-yard TD) 2017/10/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Air Force scores on 59-yard passing TD
videos.description: Arion Worthman finds Marcus Bennett wide open down the middle for an easy 59-yard touchdown, as Air Force ties Navy.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Air Force scores on 59-yard passing TD) 2017/10/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Navy scores on 40-yard passing TD
videos.description: Zach Abey connects with Malcolm Perry who high steps his way to a 40-yard touchdown, as Navy leads Air Force 28-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Navy scores on 40-yard passing TD) 2017/10/07 ESHEET
